field.name: About the work
field.value: The frustration index measures of how favorable a particular contact is relative to sets of possible interactions, normalized using the variance of the energy distribution. For initial inspection, the server classifies the individual contacts as to their frustration index value: 'minimally frustrated' 'neutral' 'highly frustrated'. Mutational frustration index results are shown on left, Configurational frustration index on the right.
